<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="h-full">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>USM Events - Eventos</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col min-h-full bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 font-sans">

    <nav class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-4 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-md">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-xl tracking-tighter">USM <span class="text-yellow-400">EVENTS</span></h1>
            <ul class="hidden md:flex space-x-6 font-medium">
                <li><a href="index.html" class="hover:text-yellow-400 transition">Inicio</a></li>
                <li><a href="eventos.html" class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">Eventos</a></li>
                <li><a href="comunidad.html" class="hover:text-yellow-400 transition">Comunidad</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto py-10 px-6">
        <header class="mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-blue-900">Cartelera de Eventos</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Explora las actividades académicas y recreativas de nuestra sede.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="flex gap-4 mb-8 overflow-x-auto pb-2">
            <button class="bg-blue-900 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm">Todos</button>
            <button class="bg-white border border-blue-900 text-blue-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-blue-50">Académicos</button>
            <button class="bg-white border border-blue-900 text-blue-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-blue-50">Deportes</button>
            <button class="bg-white border border-blue-900 text-blue-900 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-blue-50">Cultura</button>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition group">
                <div class="h-48 bg-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540575861501-7cf05a4b125a" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase">Tecnología</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-2">Feria de Innovación</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Muestra de proyectos finales de ingeniería y robótica.</p>
                    <div class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-blue-900 font-bold">20 Abr</span>
                        <button class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600">Leer más →</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition group">
                <div class="h-48 bg-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523580494863-6f3031224c94" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-green-600 uppercase">Académico</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-2">Charla: Fondos Viajes</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Información clave para postular a intercambios internacionales.</p>
                    <div class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-blue-900 font-bold">25 Abr</span>
                        <button class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600">Leer más →</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition group">
                <div class="h-48 bg-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511671782779-c97d3d27a1d4" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-purple-600 uppercase">Música</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-2">Ciclo de Jazz</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Sesión acústica en el patio al atardecer.</p>
                    <div class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-blue-900 font-bold">02 May</span>
                        <button class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600">Leer más →</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-6 px-6 border-t border-gray-800">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center md:text-left">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">© 2026 USM Events - Proyecto Taller de Programación</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
